dc_title_s: Johnson County, Iowa, 1972, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet label. Image is a photoreduction of the mosaic created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol 19103. Form of individual image numbering: 19103-372-[numbe]r, or 19103-572-[number]. Year flown: 1972. Flown by Aero-Graphics, Inc. Salt Lake City, Utah. Scale 1:38,000|Contact the Map Collection at The University of Iowa Libraries: http://www.lib.uiowa.edu/maps/contact/|Scanned at 300 ppi in Greyscale.
